data.description: This cutie has so much to offer, you won't be disappointed!  Nestled in the designed-for-Disney community by DRHorton, this Sandy Ridge gem sports a new roof, HVAC, solar panels, charger for your smart car, gym/workout space in the garage, crystal clear bubbling pool, 2 master suites with ample closet space, plus an additional bed room and bathroom. Quartz countertops, a grand sink,  and open storage will delight any cook!  Income producing property potential! Short or long-term leasing permitted.  Great location for commutes to theme parks, Champions Gate, shopping & eateries.  Buyer to assume solar panel lease ($117/month with LOW energy costs!) Please see attachments. CALL TODAY, THIS CUTIE WON'T LAST LONG!
